** neo4j
* download neo4j to the /opt, wget -O neo4j-community-2.1.5-unix.tar.gz http://neo4j.com/artifact.php?name=neo4j-community-2.1.5-unix.tar.gz
* tar xvfz neo4j-community-2.1.5-unix.tar.gz
* uncomment org.neo4j.server.webserver.address=0.0.0.0 line
* sudo ./neo4j-installer install
* sudo service neo4j-service status
* sudo service neo4j-service start
* sudo service neo4j-service stop
* sudo ./bin/neo4j-installer remove

